<br>
<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://joshragsdale.homestead.com/files/untitled.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
<br>
They still wont be to usefull at high levels, but in my opinion it makes them a viable choice in the mid levels. Earth pet hp with fire pet DS is nice with duel wielding heh. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=490410">Dalren Fieryblade of Tarew Marr</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=archangelranari@themagicianstower>Archangel Ranari</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 82<br> <font color=#333333>(12/22/02 8:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1737.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Monster Summoning: Not so useless anymore</span><hr size=1> I used Monster Summoning II against shrooms in FG.  It was cool cause I summoned a Shiknar, which I promptly had the shaman in our group enlarge for the 'coolness' factor.  This massive SOB was dishing out 30-40dps consistantly.<br>
<br>
Now, I use exclusively the 51 Earth Pet (Voceration: Earth) against the shrooms.  This pet is completely unaffected by the mushrooms slows, dots, and stuns, which are disease based.  It's so effective, in fact, that I no longer allow the warrior that I duo with to do anything.  He's plays the 60 shaman to pull/heal/buff.  I do the killing!  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ackar>Ackar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master Summoner</span><br>  Posts: 542<br> <font color=#333333>(12/22/02 9:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1737.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Monster Summoning: Not so useless anymore</span><hr size=1> MS pets have been equiping weapons for a while now, the people that say they don't just haven't used it in the past 3 months. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=yohannkoldheart>yohann koldheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#333333>(12/27/02 9:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerspells.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1737.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ms pets</span><hr size=1> its fun in CoM pullin up a black reaver and giveing him 2 swords  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promo